trans-unit.source: Called when attributes are needed for a type.
trans-unit.target: Anropas när attribut krävs för typen.

trans-unit.source: This callback enables delayed registration of metadata attributes as well as the ability to provide code that dynamically determines which attributes should be applied.
trans-unit.target: Den här återanrop kan fördröjas registrering av metadataattribut samt möjligheten att ange koden som dynamiskt bestämmer vilka attribut som ska användas.

trans-unit.source: This callback is provided to the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A> method of the <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> class.
trans-unit.target: Den här återanrop angavs för <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>metoden i <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder>klassen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder> objects can build attributes only for the type that is requesting metadata.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>objekt som kan skapa attribut endast för den typ som begär metadata.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeCallbackBuilder>
